<span id="Description"></span>
==설명==

'''기술도면 선 단축''' 도구는 양쪽 끝에서 꾸밈선이나 중심선을 단축합니다.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionShortenLineExample.png|300px]]
{{Caption|오른쪽 그림은 양쪽 끝이 단축된 중심선의 수직선 부분.}}

<span id="Usage"></span>
==용법==

# Optionally specify the delta distance with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select a single cosmetic line or centerline.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionShortenLine.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionShortenLine|Shorten Line]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionShortenLine.svg|16px]] Shorten Line}} option from the menu.
# The line is shortened at both ends.


